<scriptment id="90000" point="taro_home" localizationstatus="original" fictionaldate="2011-11-10" status="final">
	<part>
		<condition>
			<comment>The Player hired Haruka Mimieux. The Player hired Capucine Rousseau. The Player made it to the hospital. The Player failed to keep Lori and Takuya together.</comment>
			<narration>Haruka holds in both her arms her son. Knocks. On the door. It's Clarisse. It's Yuki. Yuki spots Sebastian standing behind the couch, playing with little Taro's fingers. Yuki </narration>
			<line id="1000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="fr">Hey, how's it going?</line>
			<condition>
				<choice number="1">
					<comment>The Player hired Sebastian Mimieux.</comment>
					<narration>Sebastian puts up half a hand.</narration>
					<line id="2000" speaker="sebastian" voicelang="fr">Yo.</line>
				</choice>
				<choice number="2">
					<comment>The Player did not hire Sebastian Mimieux.</comment>
					<narration>Sebastian folds his arms.</narration>
					<line id="3000" speaker="sebastian" voicelang="fr">Ugh.</line>
				</choice>
			</condition>
			<line id="4000" speaker="4000" speaker="haruka" voicelang="en">Look at my little baby boy.</line>
			<line id="5000" speaker="5000" speaker="haruka" voicelang="en">Isn't he beautiful?</line>
			<narration>Haruka smiles and continues to cradle her dear child. Yuki stares at the newborn, her eyes tearing.<comment>Cue the heartwarming music. Slowly zoom in on Taro.</comment></narration>
			<narration>Clarisse scratches her head. <comment>Cut music.</comment> Sebastian face-palms.</narration>
			<line id="6000" speaker="sebastian" voicelang="fr">"Look at my little baby boy. Isn't he beautiful?"</line>
			<line id="7000" speaker="clarisse" voicelang="fr">Oh. Yes, yes!</line>
			<line id="8000" speaker="clarisse" voicelang="fr">He reminds me of my first Third.</line>
			<line id="9000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="fr">Everyone seems to be moving on.</line>
			<line id="10000" speaker="clarisse" voicelang="fr">Too bad, though, about Lori and Takuya.</line>
			<line id="11000" speaker="clarisse" voicelang="fr">They, too, could have had a Third.</line>
			<line id="12000" speaker="clarisse" voicelang="fr">But one gave up.</line>
			<line id="13000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="fr">They gave up.</line>
			<line id="14000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="fr">Sounds familiar.</line>
			<line id="15000" speaker="clarisse" voicelang="fr">Fine, I'll take the job!</line>
			<narration>Haruka and Sebastian, in the distance, laugh as they tickle their child.</narration>
			<line id="16000" speaker="sebastian" voicelang="en">Family in.</line>
			<line id="17000" speaker="haruka" voicelang="en">Family in.</line>
		</condition>
	</part>
</scriptment>